ğŸ—ï¸ **Library-first design** for easy integration â€¢ âš¡ **10x faster** than pandas â€¢ ğŸŒŠ **Handles datasets larger than RAM** â€¢ ğŸ” **Robust quality checking** for dirty data â€¢ ğŸ—ƒï¸ **Direct database connectivity**

ğŸ“¦ **Available for both Rust and Python** â€¢ ğŸ `pip install dataprof` â€¢ ğŸ¦€ `cargo add dataprof`

